data.description: Well Maintained & Move-In Ready Country Property on 2.76 Acres! Home Offers 4 Bedroom, 2 Baths, Open Layout, Vaulted Ceilings, Split Floor Plan, Formal Dining Room, Large Eat-In Kitchen, Spacious Main Level Master En-Suite with Office, Main Level Laundry, & Ex-Large 2 Car Heated Garage! Outside, there is Plenty of Room to Roam with a Shooting Range, Apple Trees, Mostly Fenced In Private Backyard, Extra Storage with 2 Addtional Sheds, 300 Gal. Coy Pond in Front Yard, 4 Swann Surveillance Cameras - one on Each Side of Exterior of the Home with Night Vision & 14 Day DVR Recording, and Natural Spring Well Water! Updates Include AC 2023, New Cement Between Garage & House 2023, Beautiful Stone Mailbox 2020, 105 Arborvitae Privacy Trees Planted 2020, Freshly Painted Kitchen Sept 2023. Above Ground Swimming Pool & Equipment are Included!
